{"tid":1754162,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"東尼大木被爆性侵他人女友　謝罪影片曝光強辯「不記得」！","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T16:40:28.000Z","uid":80481,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3fbe073e4bcd23d8e1f1ee2ca52b7f0624e3aa","tid":1754162,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/11/25/99/7108994.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F11%2F25%2F99%2F7108994.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=4badadc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本AV男優東尼大木與另一位AV男優橫山一光，被爆出強暴別人女友，而兩人的謝罪影片更被公開，讓不少網友都很震驚。<br />\n<br />\nAV男優Pierre劍23日在推特上爆出東尼大木與橫山一光，兩人強暴他的女友，更把兩人謝罪的影片放到Youtube上，根據影片描述，他們一行人16~17日前往富士山露營，結果17日早上東尼大木與橫山一光在廚房對Pierre劍的女友進行猥褻行為得逞，之後還將女方強拖到浴室綑綁手腳，塞住嘴巴，然後強暴，在謝罪影片中兩人承諾每個月會付賠償金，希望不要將事情鬧大，但是女方不接受，指兩人沒有誠意道歉、悔改，因為兩人一直聲稱不記得，痛批兩人從事性產業，卻犯下這種性犯罪，認為兩人應該要直接被抓起來關。"},{"pid":"c56023b2e3b3da69636403af263293630e5abbf0","tid":1754162,"uid":25797,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"真係當拍AV咁搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a48685467701dd3b34fe80c4621e54fd67b1288","tid":1754162,"uid":15620,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"有得搞咁多女仲要姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae2e0c694b9cb737c58016452a34d0c90ecaa1c","tid":1754162,"uid":3189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-08-13/900/20170813001373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3